snippet.title: Goodbye Volcano High - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Goodbye Volcano High is out now on PS5, PS4, and Steam! Thank you all for your support, we are so grateful we got to make this game.

---

Goodbye Volcano High is a cinematic narrative adventure about love, change, and the end of an era. Guide Fang through their final year of high school as they try to make things right before time is up.

Fully voice-acted and starring Lachlan Watson as Fang, Ozioma Akagha as Trish, Mark Whitten as Reed, Abe Bueno-Jallad as Naser, Allegra Clark as Naomi, Sarah Elmaleh as Stella, Jensen Trani as Sage, and Dee Revilla as Rosa.

#GoodbyeVolcanoHigh #visualnovel #rhythmgames #playstation
